i\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁嬲都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無放好都唔洗扔既，雖然唔知咩黎<br />\n但佢嬲左幾耐，<br />\n超過兩個月就幾小氣<br />\n唔嬲比老母睇，下次會再嬲過<br />\n我明佢啵，另我老母都比我訓練到唔敢扔我野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢同佢父母都係鬧完一兩個鐘就會下咗道氣<br />\n<br />\n但係俾著我屋企已經趕咗我出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e077805e695b23725a68266da3c4c6d68b7522b","tid":24491,"uid":44368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大個你就係佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n突破盲點"},{"pid":"f756ea992b84f8308966bbd1c54be5a9dc7db79e","tid":24491,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"家家有本難唸的經<br />\n我都對屋企人態度幾差<br />\n其一係佢地藍絲 日日係到屌 屌到我發火<br />\n其二係佢地極度封建 牛皮燈籠點唔明<br />\n其三係我老母郁啲就喊 真心好炆 <br />\n<br />\n勸下佢係正常既<br />\n但唔洗諗到佢以後都會對你咁"},{"pid":"2c8ee3231df42d12e0ea0a831bfff5b0451a4525","tid":24491,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你有無問點解先<br />\n你咩都唔知，答唔到你啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過有次佢媽咪唔小心扔咗佢嘅 (但明明就係佢無放好) 之後就鬧到拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n望見都覺得嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁嬲都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無放好都唔洗扔既，雖然唔知咩黎<br />\n但佢嬲左幾耐，<br />\n超過兩個月就幾小氣<br />\n唔嬲比老母睇，下次會再嬲過<br />\n我明佢啵，另我老母都比我訓練到唔敢扔我野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢同佢父母都係鬧完一兩個鐘就會下咗道氣<br />\n<br />\n但係俾著我屋企已經趕咗我出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁好正常咋啵，預防勝於治療<br />\n老母唔知你咁介意，係會產生第二，三、n場悲劇"},{"pid":"ca4e1a07d8b81c2f0e6706933fffb6e791fac392","tid":24491,"uid":56835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家家有本難唸的經<br />\n我都對屋企人態度幾差<br />\n其一係佢地藍絲 日日係到屌 屌到我發火<br />\n其二係佢地極度封建 牛皮燈籠點唔明<br />\n其三係我老母郁啲就喊 真心好炆 <br />\n<br />\n勸下佢係正常既<br />\n但唔洗諗到佢以後都會對你咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我希望係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98c14f81a44d1374712c0424b53fddd4283b095","tid":24491,"uid":56835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大個你就係佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n突破盲點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好驚第時佢淨係當我係工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe8b2ae7dbe5964bd73a3dec90d1a3f6e79b4e8","tid":24491,"uid":56835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你有無問點解先<br />\n你咩都唔知，答唔到你啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過有次佢媽咪唔小心扔咗佢嘅 (但明明就係佢無放好) 之後就鬧到拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n望見都覺得嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁嬲都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無放好都唔洗扔既，雖然唔知咩黎<br />\n但佢嬲左幾耐，<br />\n超過兩個月就幾小氣<br />\n唔嬲比老母睇，下次會再嬲過<br />\n我明佢啵，另我老母都比我訓練到唔敢扔我野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢同佢父母都係鬧完一兩個鐘就會下咗道氣<br />\n<br />\n但係俾著我屋企已經趕咗我出門口<img src=\"/